{
  "stem": "935.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was not-- you know, she was not immigrating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She only got permission to visit her daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But she knew that she would not return anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not for a very-- I wasn't looking for-- I wasn't really looking for them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not for a long time, I must say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I then-- let me see, i was in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was in Holland with my older sister and her husband.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, I'd best get to where my family is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the producer-- our original producer, anyway-- he had a feeling that Belgium wouldn't be safe very long, either.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he thought that we should get out of Belgium and should get to Holland also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know why or who had applied for immigration visas to America.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was in Holland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I figured, you know, I need to go to Holland if that is supposed to come through one day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember that I literally took a taxi from Belgium and told the driver, take me to another country, and went to Holland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the only country where you still could get in-- you know, just into the country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All the other countries, especially Switzerland, was closed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You couldn't get into Switzerland anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had closed the borders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the only thing they kept open was the banks for the war promoters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were all open, all open and for the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But nobody could get in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In other words, I had run out of countries to run to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I went to Holland, to The Hague back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, at that time, my mother had already moved to the seashore of a place called Scheveningen-- not easy to pronounce.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I got my old apartment back.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
